WEBVTT

00:03.070 --> 00:04.670
Have you ever longed for someone?

00:08.375 --> 00:10.445
Did you ever dream of someone?

00:14.480 --> 00:15.580
Touched the spark...

00:20.520 --> 00:22.020
...but missed the connection?

00:25.600 --> 00:26.895
Felt so warm...

00:29.425 --> 00:31.565
...as the world turned cold?

00:37.630 --> 00:38.905
Did you fall in love...

00:43.040 --> 00:46.880
...as fast as flowers falling from trees?

00:50.450 --> 00:54.555
From the acclaimed award-winning director of "Voices of a Distant Star"...

00:57.490 --> 00:59.890
...and "The Place Promised in Our Early Days"...

01:03.430 --> 01:06.165
...comes his latest anime masterpiece.

01:13.000 --> 01:15.575
This is how fast you fall in love.

01:23.250 --> 01:25.615
5 Centimeters Per Second.

